@Node "what" "What is DefaultTool-Changer  ?"
@Next "copyright"
@Prev "Main"
@Toc  "Main"

DefaultTool-Changer is a  simple/fast program to change the Default-Tools from
all icons (WBPROJECT) in a directory. It is helpful for CD-Productions or to
change the DefaultTools on your harddisk...

 Example: you have 100 pictures with 100 icons and many DefaultTools (in some
          directories with subdirectories...), like

            c:vt
            gfx:ppshow
            hd6:mainview
            c:multiview
            sys:Utilities/Multiview
            ...


          and you need for you CD-Production

            myCDROM:c/PicViewer


          or you want only one DefaultTool for all pictures on your harddisk, like

            Multiview



          THEN YOU WILL LOVE THE PROGRAM: DefaultTool-Changer

@EndNode

